<li id="cite_note-SD1973Ap430-25"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-SD1973Ap430_25-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFSpitzerDenzer1973a">Spitzer &amp; Denzer 1973a</a>, p.&#160;430.</span>
